SelectorI - Interface in fr.sorbonne_u.cps.dht_mapreduce.interfaces.mapreduce
The functional interface SelectorI allows to define functions in the map part of the map/reduce protocol that select individual data of type ContentDataI that will be processed.
serialVersionUID - Static variable in class fr.sorbonne_u.cps.mapreduce.utils.IntInterval
default serialVersionUID.
split() - Method in class fr.sorbonne_u.cps.mapreduce.utils.IntInterval
split this interval in two equal parts, updating this interval to be the first and returning the following intervaL (the second part); this interval must contain at least four values otherwise the result will be null as the split cannot occur.
splitable() - Method in class fr.sorbonne_u.cps.mapreduce.utils.IntInterval
return true if the interval contains enough values to be split in two sub-intervals.
